      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Eemors ruunaja ar mi juhs\neem/fazzidams: Sikeima manna\nDehla Sirđs peekerrahs juhsu\nMeitai / dohdeet / luḩdsami/\nvixxam to par Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un apdrandsinajeetees ar\nuums / dohdeet mums juhsas\nMeitas / un neimneet preeksch\nms muhfäs Meitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un dsihwojeet pee mums/\nn wiffa ta Semne buhs at-\nehra juhsit Preekshâ/ mihteet/\nezzajtees / un peinajtees eeksch\nhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sikeims fazztja us\nnnas Tehwu/ un us winnas\nrah-teem: Laid es Schehlasti-\natrohmu juhsäs Azzis/ un ko\nus man fazzifeet to es doh-\nu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Prassajt papillam Kroh-\nNaudu un Dahwann / tad\nschu es / ttt ka juhs us\nn fazzifeet/ dohdcet man tik-\nto jaunu Meitu par Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Jehkaba\nbli/ Sikeimam un Eemoram/\nma Tehwam ar Wilu / un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "winno Mahfu bij fagahniijis\nun fazzija us teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mehs ne warraim sche\nLeetu darriht / ka mehs muhſa\nMahfu kahdam Wihram doh-\ndam/ kam Preeksh-Ahda irr/ jo\ntas buhtu mums weena Ne-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr eeksch ta buhfinu\nmehs jums paprahtam / ja juhs\ntohpat itt ka mehs / avgraisida-\nmi juhsit Starpâ wiffu Wih-\nrisfu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dohfin mehs jums\nmuhfas Meitas / un nemfint\nmuns juhsäs Meitas / un dsih-\nwofim ar jums kohpä/ un buh-\nfin weent Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja juhs mums ne\nklaufsfeet/ un apgraisifsfeetees/ tad\nneimfin mehs muhfu Meitu/ un\naiseefim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Wahrdi patikle\nEemoram/ un Sikeimam / Ee-\nmora Dehlam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Jauneklis ne ka-\nwejahs to Leetu darriht/ jo wiṅsch\npeemihleja Jehkaba Meitu / un\ntas bij gohdigi turrehts/pahr wif-\nfu sawu Tehwa Namnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze Eemors/ un\nSikems winna Dehls usta Pils-\nsahta Wahrtim / un runnaja ar\nsawa Pilsfahta Wihreem / un\nfazzija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee Wihri irr meerigi\nar mums/ lai tee schinni Semmē\nmiht/ un prezzejahs/ jo raugi/ tai\nSemmei irr gann plattas Roh-\n"
    }
